pageProduct.name: Voost Immunity Orange Zest Effervescent Tablets 60 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

VOOST Immunity Orange Zest contains Vitamin C 1000 mg + Zinc 10 mg. Helps support immune system health. Helps reduce the severity and duration of common cold symptoms (when taken regularly).

Get your daily VOOST

We're passionate about all things effervescent and we're on a mission to make supplements a bit more appealing! We're armed with Australia's largest range of effervescent vitamins and minerals to help you find just the right one to suit your needs.

Simple to use. Premium formulation. Great tasting.

Uses- immunity orange zest helps:
- Support healthy immune system function.
- Reduce the severity and duration of common cold symptoms (when taken regularly).
- Reduce free radicals formed in the body.
- Support general health and wellbeing.
- Support skin health and collagen formation.
- Connective tissue production.
- Increase absorption of dietary iron.

Suitable For: Vegan Friendly

Product Claims: No added dairy, soy, lactose or yeast.

Boxed Contents: 60 Effervescent Tablets (3 x 20 Tablets)

Size: 60 Tablets

Flavour: Orange zest

Warnings

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional.
Adults only. Keep out of reach of children.

Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients per tablet:
Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 1000mg
Zinc (As zinc gluconate) 10mg

Contains: Each tablet contains 380mg of sodium. Contains Sucralose. Contains less than 0.1g of sugar per tablet.

Directions

How to use:
Adults: Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200mL of water, or as directed by your health professional.

PREPARATION INSTRUCTIONS

- Start with 200mL of fresh water.
- Add one VOOST tablet & watch it fizz.
- Once dissolved, it's ready to drink!
- Experience the fizz!

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place.
Store below 25°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
